More bad news for Boeing.

The aviation giant which used to be（曾经是） one of American's crown jewels
facing a massive shakeup.

CEO Dave Calhoun announcing（宣布） he'll be stepping down
as the company faces（面临着） growing（不断增长的） safety concerns（安全隐患） surrounding their fleet of planes.
As well as an ongoing（正在进行中的） whistleblower investigation.